Class ReachablePointsMultithreaded

  • java.lang.Object
    • solver.reachablepoints.multithreaded.ReachablePointsMultithreaded
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IReachablePoints
    public class ReachablePointsMultithreaded

    Calculator class calculating success and cut off ratings as ActionsRating objects and storing the last calculated results.

      • getCalculations

        private Map<PlayerAction,​DeadlineReachablePointsCalculation> getCalculations​(RatedPredictivePlayer startPlayer,
                                                                                   Board<Cell> board,
                                                                                   FloatMatrix probabilities,
                                                                                   FloatMatrix minSteps,
                                                                                   IDeadline deadline)
        Generates DeadlineReachablePointsCalculation objects for each possible PlayerAction a given RatedPredictivePlayer can make. The objects are mapped to the performed PlayerAction and returned.
        Parameters:
        startPlayer - RatedPredictivePlayer to start the calculations with
        board - Board to check for collisions
        probabilities - FloatMatrix containing the enemy probability values
        minSteps - FloatMatrix containing the minimum enemy steps for each element
        deadline - IDeadline which must not be exceeded
        Returns:
        DeadlineReachablePointsCalculation objects mapped to the taken child PlayerAction

      • calculateMultithreaded

        private void calculateMultithreaded​(Collection<DeadlineReachablePointsCalculation> calculations,
                                    IDeadline deadline)
        Calculates each given DeadlineReachablePointsCalculation in a separate threads and joins all of them. Additionally a timer is set to interrupt running threads, which are not finished in time.
        Parameters:
        calculations - DeadlineReachablePointsCalculation objects to execute the calculation for
        deadline - IDeadline for the calculations

      • updateResults
